me.com/news/music/aaliyah-29-1369304">在 Aaliyah 于 2001 年去世</a>二十多年后发布的。那年八月，她乘坐的飞机在巴哈马群岛坠毁，不幸身亡。她与飞行员和她的团队的七名成员一起去世。 </p><figure id="attachment_3387180" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3387180" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3387180 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Aaliyah-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Aaliyah-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Aaliyah-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Aaliyah-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Aaliyah-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Aaliyah-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Aaliyah-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3387180" class="wp-caption-text">阿丽雅。图片来源：大卫·科里奥/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>她在 1994 年推出首张专辑《Age Ain&#39;t Nothing but a Number》后一举成名，并于 2001 年推出了多首热门单曲和数百万张专辑，并于 2001 年发行了同名专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-5400-327909">《Aaliyah》</a> 。</p><p> 2012 年，有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timbaland">Timbaland</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/missy-elliott">Missy Elliott</a>合作发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-8-1255721">Aaliyah 遗作专辑的报道</a>遭到<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-7-1255696">了这些音乐家的否认</a>，而传闻中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a>在 2014 年与这位已故歌手的合作项目因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-9-1257752">家人的劝阻</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-222-1231453">被取消</a>。</p><p> 2021 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd</a>在去世后邀请 Aaliyah 创作联合单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-and-the-weeknd-to-appear-on-new-collaborative-single-poison-3119944">《Poison》</a> 。第二年，Aaliyah 的叔叔确认将会发行一张由 Drake、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ne-yo">Ne-Yo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/snoop-dogg">Snoop Dogg</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">Future</a>主演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyahs-uncle-confirms-posthumous-album-unstoppable-is-coming-this-month-3129661">名为“Unstoppable”的遗作专辑</a>，尽管这一计划从未实现。</p><p> 2023 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-fans-petition-for-singer-to-be-inducted-into-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-3387179">歌迷请愿这位已故巨星入选摇滚名人堂。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aaliyah-launched-as-own-barbie-doll-on-what-would-have-been-her-own-46th-birthday-3829915">Aaliyah 在她自己的 46 岁生日那天发布了自己的芭比娃娃</a>帖子，该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
