https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_lyykeli_davidlynch_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_lyykeli_davidlynch_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025_lyykeli_davidlynch_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lykke-li">Lykke Li</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-lynch">大卫·林奇</a>去世后向他致敬，并表示他“改变了我的生活”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/david-lynch-obituary-twin-peaks-3829834">大卫·林奇 – 1946-2025：重塑电影的真正梦想家</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-dies-aged-78-3829681">昨天（1 月 16 日），他的家人</a>宣布了他的去世消息，此前据报道，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/twin-peaks"><em>《双峰》的</em></a>创作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-reportedly-died-after-being-forced-to-relocate-from-his-house-due-to-la-wildfires-3829793">因洛杉矶山火</a>“被迫搬离家”。他78岁了。</p><p>李在她的Instagram上分享了她与林奇合作的歌曲《I&#39;m Waiting Here》，收录在他2013年的专辑《The Big Dream》中，并写道：“再见我亲爱的朋友，你救了我的命，你的话语和教训将永远响起在我耳边，我想这就是这首歌的真正含义，对我来说，你是洛杉矶之王，永远在我们心中。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DE6a-KgxfwU/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow